data.description: End unit 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom townhouse located in the York Crossing neighborhood. Upstairs enjoy the two jack and jill good sized bedrooms offering access to the full bath from both rooms. Out back enjoy the fenced in yard with a storage closet allowing for a great space to entertain. New carpet upstairs. Zoned for highly sought after Grafton school district.
